# Offline-first & async

- **Local persistence is first-class** — collection codec, persisted catalog cache (`catalog_bundle_v1.json`), bundled catalog **art**; app must feel usable on poor network
- **Optimistic UI by default** — mutate `CollectionNotifier` state immediately; persist with `unawaited` save
- **Never block UI** on Firebase, Storage URL resolve, or image hydration before `_commit` / render
- **Progressive hydration** — shimmer/placeholder via `CatalogImageFromKey`; stale-while-revalidate where needed
- Browse shelf, cached catalog, search, galleries without waiting on network

## imageKey (canonical media identity)

**UI consumes `imageKey` only** via:

- `CatalogImageFromKey` / `CatalogImageDisplay` / `CatalogResolvedImage`
- `ShelfFigureThumb`, `SeriesReleaseCoverImage`, `CollectionSeriesThumbnail`
- `MarketListingImage` — **only** boundary for external listing photo URLs (market universe)

**UI must NOT:** build Storage URLs, read `ShelfFigure.imageUrl` for catalog art, await resolve before add-to-shelf.

**Media layer only:** `CatalogImageResolver`, feature `data/` mappers, codecs. `imageUrl` = optional cache/transport — UI works when null.

## Reuse (do not fork)

| Concern | Use |
|--------|-----|
| Add catalog series to shelf | `commitCatalogSeriesToShelf` → `CollectionNotifier` |
| Home release save | `addSeriesFromRelease` (sync commit) |
| Bottom sheets | `showCollectibleBottomSheet` / `showCollectionModalBottomSheet` |
| Figure gallery | `showCatalogFigureGallery` |
| Sheet scroll/dismiss | `CollectibleSheetScope` + linked `ScrollController` |

No screen-owned add flows, modal dismiss logic, or one-off image wrappers.
